    {
      "chinese": "邀請無償的志工指邀請人幫忙工作，並會殺豬宴客。吃飯時以人頭計量，然後逐一給予個人份的豬肉，並將個人分得的豬肉吃完，不得帶走，只有參與者才能分得食肉以佐餐。如果沒有豬，也可以用羊代替。這樣的行為類似相互幫忙的概念，並給予油膩的食物作為去除疲勞的報酬。",
      "ab": "Ung at mais mapana’iav hai Taudaniv mas bunun mapunhuma at mapaataz babu at mais maun hai pasanbununun masipul at sauntastasan mahusil masaiv mas maibabucia at iktuun maun. Ung at kaupa mas saidii mana’iav tu bunun a saivan mas maibabucin i Aupa na ishuul haising mais maun. Ung at mais uka dau a maibabu hai mahtu dau amin a sidi mais aiza a sidi. A maaz a siaan tu sinbizakbizak hai mungangab mas tupa tu mapaindangaz at pakaunan mas matubu i na is’uman mas ’ub’ub.",
      "order": "2",
      "sound": "https://dzywvpqnys6mw.cloudfront.net/files/2022/01/21/74518c9d8a1b2f0bb42fb0285e98c071.wav",
